Worklife balance - senior leaders will almost always be working more than 12 hours a day; No one will tell you to do overtime but culturally, you will feel the pressure to give more and you will be expected to do so especially when it comes to client expectations; If you are not working up to speed with the style of those who have been in the consulting industry for decades, you will find it hard to keep up

To get promoted, you need to be active in networks outside of your client work, and seek to continuously learn and upskill, mentor younger employees; 
You need to do all of these on top of client delivery work;
